{"type":null,"faqId":49898,"title":"为什么放大手势打开时，单手模式无法使用？","answer":"<body style=\"clear:both; padding-left:10px; padding-top:5px; padding-right:5px; padding-bottom:5px\"><div id=\"body23279683\"><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022307144__p59721402\">因为单手模式跟放大手势都是对屏幕触摸动作的识别来进行相应的操作，两者无法同时使用。在放大手势开启时，无法使用单手模式。请按如下方法关闭放大手势功能：</p><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022307144__p621706\">设置 &gt; 全部设置 &gt; 辅助功能 &gt; 放大手势，关闭即可。如下图所示：</p><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022307144__p5595356\"><span><img src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/79bf3_vav9m.png\" title=\"点击放大\" class=\"imgResize\"></span><span><img src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/79bf4_lvkhz.png\" title=\"点击放大\" class=\"imgResize\"></span></p><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022307144__p50358210\"></p><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022307144__p50570707\"></p></div><div><div class=\"familylinks\"></div></div></body>","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"zh-cn_topic_0022307144","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1448627796000,"seriesProductName":"NXT-AL10A,NXT-AL10B,NXT-AL10C,NXT-CL00A,NXT-DL00A,NXT-TL00A","visitedTimes":3,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"放大手势,打开,单手模式,无法使用","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}